HART
v.
DARWISH S243062 Supreme Court of California. MAY 9, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Transferred to CA 2/2 after hold. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for Parrish v. Latham & Watkins (2017) 3 Cal.5th 767, 221 Cal.Rptr.3d 432, 400 P.3d 1, is hereby dismissed ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1) ). Accordingly, respondents' 'Motion to Dismiss Review,' filed on April 26, 2018, is dismissed as moot.
